CUGCUGCUGCUGCUGCUG CAGCAGCAGCAG&CAGCAGCAGCAG&CUGCUGCUGCUGCUGCUG&CAGCAGCAGCAG&CUGCUGCUGCUGCUGCUG&CAGCAGCAGCAG&CUGCUGCUGCUGCUGCUG&CAGCAGCAGCAG&CAGCAGCAGCAG&CUGCUGCUGCUGCUGCUG\
) } def
/len { sequence length } bind def

